    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0004",
      "text": "Extended Link Services",
      "bbox": [
        114.0,
        57.38,
        237.38,
        69.64
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0005",
      "text": "4.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        109.88,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0006",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        82.97,
        178.18,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0007",
      "text": "An Extended Link Service (ELS) request solicits a destination Nx_Port to perform a function.  An ELS",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        540.02,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0008",
      "text": "reply shall be transmitted in response to an ELS request, unless otherwise specified.  Each request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.04,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0009",
      "text": "or reply is composed of a single Sequence with the ELS_Command code being specified in the first",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.06,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0010",
      "text": "word of the Payload of the first frame of the Sequence. If Zoning is active in the Fabric (see FC-GS-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.97,
        540.18,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0011",
      "text": "5), an ELS response from a well-known address (e.g., the Domain Controller) shall only include data",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.97,
        539.96,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0012",
      "text": "relating to Nx_Ports that are in the same zone(s) as the requesting Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        432.0,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0013",
      "text": "Each Sequence may be composed of one or more frames.  Normal rules for Exchange and Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.13,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0014",
      "text": "quence management apply to ELS frames, Sequences, and Exchanges.  An Accept (LS_ACC) to an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.9,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0015",
      "text": "ELS shall terminate the Exchange by setting the Last Sequence bit to one on the last frame of the re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.07,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0016",
      "text": "ply.  An ELS request and the corresponding reply shall be performed within a single Exchange. Nor-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        540.05,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0017",
      "text": "mal rules for Exchange and Sequence mange as defined in FC-FS-2 shall apply.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        452.04,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0018",
      "text": "The TYPE field for ELS frames shall be set to 01h.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        319.4,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0019",
      "text": "The R_CTL shall be set as specified in table 2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        302.67,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0020",
      "text": "The first byte of the Payload (ELS_Command code) of the request or reply Sequence shall be as",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        539.95,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0021",
      "text": "shown in table 3.  The remainder of the Payload is ELS unique.  Subsequent frames, if any, for a re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.94,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0022",
      "text": "quest or reply Sequence shall only contain additional Payload in the Payload field (i.e., the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.94,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0023",
      "text": "ELS_Command code is not repeated in each frame).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        329.22,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0024",
      "text": "4.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        109.88,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0025",
      "text": "Extended Link Service requests",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        550.96,
        270.96,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0026",
      "text": "4.2.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        118.21,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0027",
      "text": "Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        128.21,
        574.96,
        186.51,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0028",
      "text": "A Sequence Initiator shall transmit an ELS Sequence in order to solicit the destination Nx_Port to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        539.97,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0029",
      "text": "perform a link-level function or service.  Unless otherwise noted, Extended Link Service requests",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.99,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0030",
      "text": "shall not be issued prior to completion of N_Port Login.  Table 3 applies to ELSs sent to or received",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.89,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0031",
      "text": "by all valid addresses, including well known addresses.  FLOGI is required before all ELSs if a Fabric",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.0,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0032",
      "text": "is present.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        142.08,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0033",
      "text": "The LFA is used as the destination ID (D_ID) in the LINIT and LSTS ELS Request Sequences, and is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        540.01,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0034",
      "text": "used as the source ID (S_ID) in the Reply Sequences. No other Sequences shall be directed to a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        539.93,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p036_s0035",
      "text": "LFA.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        695.02,
        117.07,
        706.13
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
